notes
I am a PhD student with Kjellmar Oksavik as my supervisor. I need data for my
PhD thesis "Dynamics of mesoscale ionospheric irregularities over Svalbard".
Will be measuring Ne and Te with 32m and 42m for use in a multi-instrument study
looking at ionospheric GPS scintillations in the nightside polar cap over
Svalbard. I request 20 hours of Norway's time, 18-23 UT from 22 February to 25
February inclusive.
